Subject: [PATCH 04/22] Reset DMS state when requests finish

Add class-level registry of DMSFlashAttentionImpl instances so that
GPUModelRunner.finish_requests() can reset per-request DMS state
(circular buffer, seq_lens, free slots) across all layers before
the request index is freed. Prevents stale state accumulation.

