Date: Thu, 20 Mar 2026 11:51:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 14/22] Disable prefix caching when DMS is active

DMS compacts the KV cache per-request, which would corrupt shared
prefix blocks. Explicitly disable prefix caching at model init
with an info log message.

---
