Subject: [PATCH 16/22] Multi-request batching: fix state reset + decode buffer
 resize

- Reset DMS state for finished requests in v1 gpu_model_runner
  (was missing, causing state leak between sequential batches)
- Grow Split-K intermediate buffer when batch size increases
  (fixed illegal memory access with 8+ concurrent requests)
- Add TestMultiRequestBatching: 4 tests covering concurrent,
  sequential, mixed-length, and 8-request throughput scenarios

